column5: I'm not sure how authentic this is, but is funny.  http://www.telegraph.co.uk/motoring/motoringvideo/9927554/Nascar-racer-Jeff-Gordon-goes-undercover-in-test-drive-viral.html
Yeah probably fake as there was defiantly right hand turns involved, lol.
Fake or not - that is halarious. Patsy just bought a Camero a couple months ago and she's rolling on the floor laughing.
Fake or not - that is hilarious. x 2
Oh, sorry, I didn't see this post.  Mine can be deleted then  Definately made me laugh this morning
